            </div>

            <div class="question" id="057_each">
                What does "<%- skillFormat("⟪ENTER⟫") %> one Member of each Member of <span class="redtext">"Guilty Kiss"</span>"
                mean?
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                It means that you may <%- skillFormat("⟪ENTER⟫") %> up to one <span class="redtext">"Riko"</span>, one
                <span class="redtext">"Yoshiko"</span>, and one <span class="redtext">"Mari"</span>. That means you can
                for example <%- skillFormat("⟪ENTER⟫ three Members, one of each, or ⟪ENTER⟫") %> only a <span
                        class="redtext">"Riko"</span> and a <span class="redtext">"Yoshiko"</span> card.
            </div>
            <div class="question" id="057_other">
                What happens if non-<span class="redtext">"Guilty Kiss"</span> Members are participating in
                this <%- skillFormat("⟪LIVE⟫") %>?
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                As long as <span class="redtext">"Riko"</span>, <span class="redtext">"Yoshiko"</span> and <span
                        class="redtext">"Mari"</span> have joined this <%- skillFormat("⟪LIVE⟫") %>, the Skill can be
                used no matter what other Members are participating.
            </div>

            <h5><a href="/card/LL07-058/">LL07-058 "Landing action Yeah!!"</a></h5>
            <div class="seealso">
                See also: <a href="/faq/general#members_on_stage">What does "Members on Stage" mean?</a>
            </div>

            <h5><a href="/card/LL07-059/">LL07-059 "G Senjou no Cinderella"</a></h5>
            <div class="question" id="059_each">
                If multiple Lives use this Song card, is the Live Points goal increased for each one?
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                Yes. One point is added for each card used.
            </div>
            <div class="question" id="059_increase_first">
                I performed a ⟪LIVE⟫ with this Song when the Live Points goal was 9, and hit 9 Live Points. Do I win?
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                No. The Live Points goal increased by one, so you need another point.
            </div>
            <div class="question" id="059_win">
                If playing with three or more players, what happens if a Live using this Song card is performed when one
                of the players already won with 9 Live Points?
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                The players who have already won will remain winners. The Live Points goal increases for the remaining
                players.
            </div>
            <div class="question" id="059_out">
                The player who used this Song card for a Live has won. Is the <%- skillFormat("[While Live]") %> Skill
                still active after that?
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                Yes. <%- skillFormat("[While Live]") %> Skills will be active until the end of the game.
            </div>

