            <h5><a href="/card/LL07-064/">LL07-064 "Chika Takami"</a> to <a href="/card/LL07-081/">LL07-081 "Ruby
                    Kurosawa"</a></h5>
            <div class="question" id="064">
                If multiple players have starting Members with <%- skillFormat("[Starter]") %> Skills, in what order
                should the Skills be used?
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                Skills are used in the turn order decided at the start of the match. Once everyone's
                <%- skillFormat("[Starter]") %> Skills have been resolved, the player taking the first turn begins.
            </div>
